程序包net.minecraftforge.common.property的分层结构

程序包分层结构:
  • 所有程序包

类分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minecraft.block.state.BlockStateBase (implements net.minecraft.block.state.IBlockState)
      • net.minecraft.block.state.BlockStateContainer.StateImplementation
        • net.minecraftforge.common.property.ExtendedBlockState.ExtendedStateImplementation (implements net.minecraftforge.common.property.IExtendedBlockState)
    • net.minecraft.block.state.BlockStateContainer
      • net.minecraftforge.common.property.ExtendedBlockState
    • net.minecraftforge.common.property.Properties
    • net.minecraftforge.common.property.Properties.PropertyAdapter<V> (implements net.minecraftforge.common.property.IUnlistedProperty<V>)
    • net.minecraftforge.common.property.PropertyFloat (implements net.minecraftforge.common.property.IUnlistedProperty<V>)

接口分层结构

  • net.minecraft.block.state.IBlockBehaviors
    • net.minecraft.block.state.IBlockState (并 extends net.minecraft.block.state.IBlockProperties)
      • net.minecraftforge.common.property.IExtendedBlockState
  • net.minecraft.block.state.IBlockProperties
    • net.minecraft.block.state.IBlockState (并 extends net.minecraft.block.state.IBlockBehaviors)
      • net.minecraftforge.common.property.IExtendedBlockState
  • net.minecraftforge.common.property.IUnlistedProperty<V>
